  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your animal companion can terrify as well as fight.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Handle Animal 4 ranks, Intimidate 4 ranks, animal companion or mount class feature.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Your animal companion or mount gains Intimidate as a class skill. It can attempt to demoralize an opponent using the Intimidate skill as a move action on the same round that it damages an opponent with a natural attack.<br/><br/><b>Normal</b><br/>Animal companions and mounts with an Intelligence score of 2 or less must select feats from a limited list.<br/><br/><b>Special</b><br/>Your animal companion can select the Dazzling Display and Shatter Defenses feats if it meets the prerequisites. This feat does not allow your animal companion to use Intimidate to make a target friendly or gain their assistance.",
